about.summary: A jazzy skin for the Django Admin-Interface.

name: django-grappelli
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "2.13.1" %}

package:
  name: django-grappelli
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/d/django-grappelli/django-grappelli-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8f3939a620aa2283f38b945b9963501b15c1b26abe03414fb48576765d59942d

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - django

test:
  imports:
    - grappelli
    - grappelli.templatetags
    - grappelli.tests
    - grappelli.views

about:
  home: http://django-grappelli.readthedocs.org
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'A jazzy skin for the Django Admin-Interface.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - kwilcox
    - ocefpaf
